summary: Like to play as Conjurer? Then you probably will like this :)
descriptionHtml:
Yeah I decided to make this because I want more summonable things to Skyrim and I really like to play as mage/conjurer so I ended up this:) Im hoping to get more time to myself so I start to make spells from Oblivion because there was so many spells and I really enjoyed them:)
Hope you like it and remember to Endorse and give some feedback, if you want you could give me suggestions what to do BUT dont suggest to improve my Honeyside Improvement or Faem Hall player home because CK crash when I try to load those ;(

============================================================================================
